Depends: ruby, pkg-config, libxml2, libxslt, gumbo-parser, gumbo-parser-static
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://nokogiri.org/
Description: Ruby gem for HTML/XML parsing (system libraries version)
 Nokogiri is an HTML/XML parser for Ruby that uses system libraries.
 This package ensures proper installation with Termux's libraries.
